        conseils: "Val d'Europe shopping centre is open Monday-Saturday 10am-9pm and Sunday 11am-7pm. La Vallée Village is open daily 10am-7pm (8pm Saturday). Sea Life aquarium is open daily 10am-5:30pm on weekdays and 10am-6pm at weekends. Sea Life tickets cost €21.50 adult and €17.50 child (3-11) at the counter, but are often available at €16 online. A family ticket (2 adults + 2 children) is €60. The Sea Life visit takes about 1.5 hours including touch pools. For La Vallée Village, the best deals come during additional private sales (on top of permanent discounts). Non-EU tourists can benefit from tax refunds (about 12% additional discount) at the Pablo bureau in La Vallée Village. Plan a half-day for shopping and Sea Life, or a full day if also exploring Disneyland Paris 5 minutes away. For lunch, the shopping centre food court offers wide variety (budget €10-15), and La Vallée Village has more upscale restaurants.",
